data.description: Come see this beautiful, well-maintained home in Planter's Row!  Conveniently located in Maudlin this large 4 bedroom, 2 1/2 bath house offers a great amount of space.  Upon entering the home you're greeted by a beautiful 2 story foyer and open staircase.  Located just off the foyer the open concept formal living room and dining room are perfect for entertaining.  The kitchen features a breakfast area, white raised panel cabinetry, granite countertops, a tiled backsplash, pantry closet, a full suite of appliances and a built-in desk.  The kitchen opens up to the expansive den area that includes a wood burning fireplace and outdoor deck overlooking the backyard.  The master bedroom is located on the second floor and includes a tray ceiling, master bath with double vanity, walk-in shower with bench seating, and a huge walk-in closet.  The three other bedrooms offer generous size closets and have a full bath with a double vanity adjacent to them.  Other features include: a two-car attached garage, double paned windows, multiple storage areas, a corner lot with trees, a club House with pool, two tennis courts and kid's playground.  Insulation and a moisture barrier have recently been added underneath the home.  Zoned Greenbriar Elementary, Hillcrest Middle and Hillcrest High.  Access to I-385 and I-85 are two miles away.  Downtown Greenville, and downtown Simpsonville are minutes away and offer outdoor entertainment, festivals, restaurants, boutiques, and more!  Please verify any information you deem important.
